box model :

 Note :  in HTML every element is a box 

 For  every box below CSS properties are avialable .

   1. width : horizontal space  
   2. height : vertical space 

   3. padding : inner space of an element 

   this space is between content and element edge
    padding :  10px : all sides 
    padding : 10px  20px  (top-bottom  right-left)
    padding : 10px 20px 30px ( top , right-left, bottom)
    padding : 10px 20px 30px 40px ( top right bottom left) 

    padding-top : 20px;
    padding-right: 20px
    padding-bottom: 20px
    padding-left: 20px


   4. margin : outer space  of an element 
    A space between border to border of two differenet elements 

    margin :  10px : all sides 
    margin : 10px  20px  (top-bottom  right-left)
    margin : 10px 20px 30px ( top , right-left, bottom)
    margin : 10px 20px 30px 40px ( top right bottom left) 

    margin-top : 20px;
    margin-right: 20px
    margin-bottom: 20px
    margin-left: 20px



   5. border : decoration

        border-width : 4px
        border-style : solid
        border-color : red

        boder : 2px solid red;
        border : border-width  border-style border-color;













   6. outline -extra decoration
        outline-width
        outline-style
        outline-color
